<p>
<span style="font-family: trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong>The Castle Inn</strong>, Pengenffordd, near talgarth ld3 0eP www.brecon-beaconsaccommodation.co.uk
<br/>tel: 01874 711353 is located on the A479 between Talgarth and Crickhowell. The car park is on the left hand side. Â£1 is charged for parking which should be paid at the Inn. All parking monies are donated to charity.
<br/>
<br/>
<strong>Castell Dinas</strong>â€“ so179301 is accessed by a footpath leading from the Castle Inn car park. It is recommended to take an os map.
<br/>
<br/>
<strong>The Black Mountains Gliding Club</strong>, the airfield, Talgarth ld3 0eJ www.blackmountainsglidingclub. co.uk tel: 01874 711463 is signed off the a479 on the left hand side between talgarth and Crickhowell.</span></span></p>
<h3>Facilities and Access</h3>
<p>
